Vars.var_description: Objects added to a run loop using this value as the mode are monitored by all run loop modes that have been declared as a member of the set of “common" modes; see the description of CFRunLoopAddCommonMode(_:_:) for details.
The mode to deal with input sources other than NSConnection objects.
The mode set while tracking in controls takes place. You can use this mode to add timers that fire during tracking.
